,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T21:13:15.000Z","msg":"Arsenal FC&rlm; @Arsenal <br />\n It's never over with him on the pitch...<br />\n<br />\n7️⃣ of @_OlivierGiroud_'s last 🔟 goals for us have come in the 80th minute or later <br />\n<br />\n#NaNaNaNaa<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DG-kXV-XUAAP9F_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDG-kXV-XUAAP9F_.jpg&h=32bf9b00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6db3a76ac93086bbcb98c962f5d0f67f3de70527","tid":356142,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T21:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>.@LacazetteAlex on his PL debut<br />\n1st goal for Arsenal<br />\n3 shots, 2 on target<br />\n3 chances created<br />\n21 passes, 90.5% accuracy</blockquote><br />\n入球太少，少過華迪，起碼入3球，水貨"},{"pid":"399251219387390eb33421b396b94d9aacd8ff32","tid":356142,"uid":8404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T21:13:24.000Z","msg":"1617<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推另外果個啦"},{"pid":"ffa67fe3bb0b527f10d5c5d6a3a67dcb1f76d7b1","tid":356142,"uid":37604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T21:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>16-17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是旦啦 唔講咁多 雲加好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2519c1c77b3e9822f9f1d5438fd811b94af11db","tid":356142,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T21:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DG-ld9TUI